{"type":"message","id":"92aacb1b","parentId":"7cb077dc","timestamp":"2026-03-03T01:32:06.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建实现指南文档，把具体的代码实现细节和开发步骤整理出来。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在创建实现指南文档：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3f51fc29d7a24827a9efea15","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Project X-Ray 实现指南\n\n_开发步骤 + 核心代码实现_\n\n**版本：** v1.0  \n**创建日期：** 2026-03-03  \n**作者：** 小虾 🦐\n\n---\n\n## 📋 开发步骤\n\n### Step 1: 初始化项目\n\n```bash\n# 创建技能目录\nmkdir G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\project-xray\ncd G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\project-xray\n\n# 初始化 npm 项目\nnpm init -y\n\n# 安装依赖\nnpm install commander glob fs-extra dependency-tree handlebars ora chalk\n```\n\n### Step 2: 创建目录结构\n\n```bash\nmkdir bin lib templates detectors references\n```\n\n### Step 3: 实现核心模块\n\n按以下顺序开发：\n1. `lib/tech-stack-detector.js` - 技术栈识别\n2. `lib/scanner.js` - 项目扫描器\n3. `lib/analyzer.js` - 架构分析器\n4. `lib/docgen.js` - 文档生成器\n5. `bin/xray.js` - CLI 入口\n\n---\n\n## 💻 核心代码实现\n\n### 1. 技术栈识别器 (lib/tech-stack-detector.js)\n\n```javascript\n/**\n * 技术栈识别器\n * \n * @author jixiang\n */\n\nconst fs = require('fs-extra');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nclass TechStackDetector {\n  constructor(rootPath) {\n    this.rootPath = rootPath;\n  }\n\n  async detect() {\n    const result = {\n      language: 'unknown',\n      framework: 'unknown',\n      dependencies: [],\n      configFiles: []\n    };\n\n    // 检测 Node.js 项目\n    if (await this.hasFile('package.json')) {\n      result.language = 'TypeScript/JavaScript';\n      const pkg = await this.readPackageJson();\n      result.framework = this.detectNodeFramework(pkg);\n      result.dependencies = this.extractKeyDependencies(pkg);\n      result.configFiles.push('package.json');\n    }\n\n    // 检测 Java 项目\n    if (await this.hasFile('pom.xml')) {\n      result.language = 'Java';\n      result.framework = 'Spring Boot'; // 简化，实际需要解析 XML\n      result.configFiles.push('pom.xml');\n    } else if (await this.hasFile('build.gradle')) {\n      result.language = 'Java';\n      result.framework = 'Spring Boot/Gradle';\n      result.configFiles.push('build.gradle');\n    }\n\n    // 检测 Python 项目\n    if (await this.hasFile('requirements.txt')) {\n      result.language = 'Python';\n      result.framework = this.detectPythonFramework();\n      result.configFiles.push('requirements.txt');\n    }\n\n    // 检测 Go 项目\n    if (await this.hasFile('go.mod')) {\n      result.language = 'Go';\n      result.framework = this.detectGoFramework();\n      result.configFiles.push('go.mod');\n    }\n\n    return result;\n  }\n\n  async hasFile(filename) {\n    const filePath = path.join(this.rootPath, filename);\n    return await fs.pathExists(filePath);\n  }\n\n  async readPackageJson() {\n    const pkgPath = path.join(this.rootPath, 'package.json');\n    const content = await fs.readFile(pkgPath, 'utf-8');\n    return JSON.parse(content);\n  }\n\n  detectNodeFramework(pkg) {\n    const deps = {\n      ...pkg.dependencies,\n      ...pkg.devDependencies\n    };\n\n    if (deps['@nestjs/core']) return 'NestJS';\n    if (deps['express']) return 'Express';\n    if (deps['koa']) return 'Koa';\n    if (deps['fastify']) return 'Fastify';\n    if (deps['next']) return 'Next.js';\n    if (deps['nuxt']) return 'Nuxt.js';\n    if (deps['react']) return 'React';\n    if (deps['vue']) return 'Vue';\n\n    return 'Node.js';\n  }\n\n  extractKeyDependencies(pkg) {\n    const deps = {\n      ...pkg.dependencies,\n      ...pkg.devDependencies\n    };\n\n    // 提取关键依赖（数据库、ORM、认证等）\n    const keyDeps = [];\n    const patterns = {\n      database: ['pg', 'mysql', 'mongodb', 'mongoose', 'typeorm', 'sequelize', 'prisma'],\n      auth: ['passport', 'jsonwebtoken', 'bcrypt', 'bcryptjs'],\n      testing: ['jest', 'mocha', 'chai', 'vitest'],\n      build: ['webpack', 'vite', 'rollup', 'esbuild']\n    };\n\n    for (const [category, libs] of Object.entries(patterns)) {\n      const found = libs.filter(lib => deps[lib]);\n      if (found.length > 0) {\n        keyDeps.push({ category, libs: found });\n      }\n    }\n\n    return keyDeps;\n  }\n\n  detectPythonFramework() {\n    // 简化实现，实际需要解析 requirements.txt\n    return 'Django/Flask/FastAPI';\n  }\n\n  detectGoFramework() {\n    // 简化实现，实际需要解析 go.mod\n    return 'Gin/Echo/Fiber';\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = TechStackDetector;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. 项目扫描器 (lib/scanner.js)\n\n```javascript\n/**\n * 项目扫描器\n * \n * @author jixiang\n */\n\nconst fs = require('fs-extra');\nconst path = require('path');\nconst glob = require('glob');\nconst TechStackDetector = require('./tech-stack-detector');\n\nclass ProjectScanner {\n  constructor(rootPath) {\n    this.rootPath = rootPath;\n    this.ignorePatterns = [\n      'node_modules',\n      '.git',\n      'dist',\n      'build',\n      'target',\n      '__pycache__',\n      '.idea',\n      '.vscode',\n      'coverage',\n      '*.log'\n    ];\n  }\n\n  async scan() {\n    const techStackDetector = new TechStackDetector(this.rootPath);\n    const techStack = await techStackDetector.detect();\n\n    const fileStructure = await this.scanDirectory();\n    const stats = await this.countLines();\n    const architecture = await this.detectArchitecture();\n\n    return {\n      projectName: path.basename(this.rootPath),\n      rootPath: this.rootPath,\n      techStack,\n      fileStructure,\n      stats,\n      architecture\n    };\n  }\n\n  async scanDirectory() {\n    const files = [];\n    \n    for (const pattern of ['**/*']) {\n      const matches = glob.sync(pattern, {\n        cwd: this.rootPath,\n        ignore: this.ignorePatterns,\n        nodir: true\n      });\n      files.push(...matches);\n    }\n\n    // 生成目录树\n    const tree = this.buildDirectoryTree(files);\n    return tree;\n  }\n\n  buildDirectoryTree(files) {\n    const tree = {};\n    \n    for (const file of files) {\n      const parts = file.split(path.sep);\n      let current = tree;\n      \n      for (let i = 0; i < parts.length - 1; i++) {\n        const part = parts[i];\n        if (!current[part]) {\n          current[part] = {};\n        }\n        current = current[part];\n      }\n      \n      // 添加文件\n      const filename = parts[parts.length - 1];\n      current[filename] = null;\n    }\n\n    return tree;\n  }\n\n  async countLines() {\n    const stats = {\n      totalFiles: 0,\n      totalLines: 0,\n      codeLines: 0,\n      testFiles: 0,\n      byExtension: {}\n    };\n\n    const files = glob.sync('**/*', {\n      cwd: this.rootPath,\n      ignore: this.ignorePatterns,\n      nodir: true\n    });\n\n    for (const file of files) {\n      stats.totalFiles++;\n      \n      const ext = path.extname(file);\n      if (!stats.byExtension[ext]) {\n        stats.byExtension[ext] = { files: 0, lines: 0 };\n      }\n      stats.byExtension[ext].files++;\n\n      // 识别测试文件\n      if (file.includes('.test.') || file.includes('.spec.') || file.includes('test/')) {\n        stats.testFiles++;\n      }\n\n      // 统计代码行数（简化实现，实际可以读取文件）\n      const lines = await this.countFileLines(path.join(this.rootPath, file));\n      stats.totalLines += lines;\n      stats.codeLines += Math.floor(lines * 0.8); // 估算 80% 是代码\n      stats.byExtension[ext].lines += lines;\n    }\n\n    return stats;\n  }\n\n  async countFileLines(filePath) {\n    try {\n      const content = await fs.readFile(filePath, 'utf-8');\n      return content.split('\\n').length;\n    } catch {\n      return 0;\n    }\n  }\n\n  async detectArchitecture() {\n    const patterns = {\n      'Layered': ['controllers', 'services', 'models', 'repositories'],\n      'MVC': ['controllers', 'views', 'models'],\n      'Clean Architecture': ['entities', 'usecases', 'interfaces', 'infrastructure'],\n      'Microservices': ['docker-compose.yml', 'k8s', 'services']\n    };\n\n    const dirs = await fs.readdir(this.rootPath);\n    const foundPatterns = [];\n\n    for (const [style, markers] of Object.entries(patterns)) {\n      const matches = markers.filter(m => dirs.includes(m));\n      if (matches.length >= 2) {\n        foundPatterns.push({ style, matches, confidence: matches.length / markers.length });\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 返回置信度最高的\n    if (foundPatterns.length > 0) {\n      foundPatterns.sort((a, b) => b.confidence - a.confidence);\n      const best = foundPatterns[0];\n      return {\n        style: best.style,\n        confidence: Math.round(best.confidence * 100),\n        patterns: best.matches\n      };\n    }\n\n    return {\n      style: 'Unknown',\n      confidence: 0,\n      patterns: []\n    };\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = ProjectScanner;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Mermaid 图表生成器 (lib/mermaid-gen.js)\n\n```javascript\n/**\n * Mermaid 图表生成器\n * \n * @author jixiang\n */\n\nclass MermaidGenerator {\n  // 生成模块依赖图\n  generateModuleDependencyGraph(modules) {\n    let mermaid = 'graph TD\\n';\n    \n    // 添加节点\n    for (const module of modules) {\n      const nodeId = this.sanitizeId(module.name);\n      mermaid += `    ${nodeId}[${module.name}]\\\\n`;\n    }\n\n    // 添加边\n    for (const module of modules) {\n      const fromId = this.sanitizeId(module.name);\n      for (const dep of module.dependencies) {\n        const toId = this.sanitizeId(dep);\n        mermaid += `    ${fromId} --> ${toId}\\\\n`;\n      }\n    }\n\n    return mermaid;\n  }\n\n  // 生成数据流图\n  generateDataFlowDiagram(flows) {\n    let mermaid = 'graph LR\\n';\n    \n    for (const flow of flows) {\n      const fromId = this.sanitizeId(flow.from);\n      const toId = this.sanitizeId(flow.to);\n      const label = flow.label ? `|${flow.label}|` : '';\n      mermaid += `    ${fromId} ${label}--> ${toId}\\\\n`;\n    }\n\n    return mermaid;\n  }\n\n  // 生成序列图\n  generateSequenceDiagram(steps) {\n    let mermaid = 'sequenceDiagram\\\\n';\n    \n    // 提取参与者\n    const participants = [...new Set(steps.map(s => s.actor))];\n    for (const actor of participants) {\n      mermaid += `    participant ${this.sanitizeId(actor)}\\\\n`;\n    }\n\n    // 添加消息\n    for (const step of steps) {\n      const from = this.sanitizeId(step.from);\n      const to = this.sanitizeId(step.to);\n      const msg = step.message;\n      mermaid += `    ${from}->>${to}: ${msg}\\\\n`;\n    }\n\n    return mermaid;\n  }\n\n  sanitizeId(str) {\n    return str.replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9]/g, '_');\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = MermaidGenerator;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. 文档生成器 (lib/docgen.js) - 简化版\n\n```javascript\n/**\n * 文档生成器\n * \n * @author jixiang\n */\n\nconst fs = require('fs-extra');\nconst path = require('path');\nconst Handlebars = require('handlebars');\nconst MermaidGenerator = require('./mermaid-gen');\n\nclass DocumentGenerator {\n  constructor(templateDir) {\n    this.templateDir = templateDir;\n    this.mermaidGen = new MermaidGenerator();\n  }\n\n  async generateAll(analysis, outputDir) {\n    await fs.ensureDir(outputDir);\n    await fs.ensureDir(path.join(outputDir, 'diagrams'));\n    await fs.ensureDir(path.join(outputDir, 'inventory'));\n\n    // 生成 6 个核心文档\n    await this.generateQuickStart(analysis, outputDir);\n    await this.generateOverview(analysis, outputDir);\n    await this.generateArchitectureGuide(analysis, outputDir);\n    await this.generateCoreModules(analysis, outputDir);\n    await this.generateCodeNavigation(analysis, outputDir);\n    await this.generateGlossary(analysis, outputDir);\n\n    // 生成 JSON 清单\n    await this.generateInventory(analysis, outputDir);\n  }\n\n  async generateQuickStart(analysis, outputDir) {\n    const template = await this.loadTemplate('00-quick-start.md.template');\n    const content = template({\n      projectName: analysis.projectName,\n      techStack: analysis.techStack,\n      installCommand: this.getInstallCommand(analysis.techStack),\n      startCommand: this.getStartCommand(analysis.techStack)\n    });\n    await fs.writeFile(path.join(outputDir, '00-quick-start.md'), content);\n  }\n\n  async generateOverview(analysis, outputDir) {\n    const template = await this.loadTemplate('01-project-overview.md.template');\n    const content = template(analysis);\n    await fs.writeFile(path.join(outputDir, '01-project-overview.md'), content);\n  }\n\n  async generateArchitectureGuide(analysis, outputDir) {\n    const template = await this.loadTemplate('02-architecture-guide.md.template');\n    \n    // 生成 Mermaid 图\n    const mermaidGraph = this.mermaidGen.generateModuleDependencyGraph(analysis.modules || []);\n    await fs.writeFile(\n      path.join(outputDir, 'diagrams', 'module-dependency.mmd'),\n      mermaidGraph\n    );\n\n    const content = template({\n      ...analysis,\n      mermaidGraph\n    });\n    await fs.writeFile(path.join(outputDir, '02-architecture-guide.md'), content);\n  }\n\n  async generateCoreModules(analysis, outputDir) {\n    const template = await this.loadTemplate('03-core-modules.md.template');\n    const content = template(analysis);\n    await fs.writeFile(path.join(outputDir, '03-core-modules.md'), content);\n  }\n\n  async generateCodeNavigation(analysis, outputDir) {\n    const template = await this.loadTemplate('04-code-navigation.md.template');\n    const content = template(analysis);\n    await fs.writeFile(path.join(outputDir, '04-code-navigation.md'), content);\n  }\n\n  async generateGlossary(analysis, outputDir) {\n    const template = await this.loadTemplate('05-glossary.md.template');\n    const content = template(analysis);\n    await fs.writeFile(path.join(outputDir, '05-glossary.md'), content);\n  }\n\n  async generateInventory(analysis, outputDir) {\n    await fs.writeFile(\n      path.join(outputDir, 'inventory', 'tech-stack.json'),\n      JSON.stringify(analysis.techStack, null, 2)\n    );\n    await fs.writeFile(\n      path.join(outputDir, 'inventory', 'file-structure.json'),\n      JSON.stringify(analysis.fileStructure, null, 2)\n    );\n  }\n\n  async loadTemplate(name) {\n    const templatePath = path.join(this.templateDir, name);\n    const content = await fs.readFile(templatePath, 'utf-8');\n    return Handlebars.compile(content);\n  }\n\n  getInstallCommand(techStack) {\n    if (techStack.language.includes('Node')) return 'npm install';\n    if (techStack.language === 'Python') return 'pip install -r requirements.txt';\n    if (techStack.language === 'Java') return 'mvn install';\n    if (techStack.language === 'Go') return 'go mod download';\n    return '安装依赖';\n  }\n\n  getStartCommand(techStack) {\n    if (techStack.language.includes('Node')) return 'npm run dev';\n    if (techStack.language === 'Python') return 'python manage.py runserver';\n    if (techStack.language === 'Java') return 'mvn spring-boot:run';\n    if (techStack.language === 'Go') return 'go run main.go';\n    return '启动项目';\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = DocumentGenerator;\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 模板示例 (templates/00-quick-start.md.template)\n\n```markdown\n# {{projectName}} - 快速上手指南\n\n_5 分钟快速启动项目_\n\n---\n\n## 📋 环境要求\n\n- Node.js >= 18.x\n- npm >= 9.x\n- PostgreSQL >= 14.x\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速启动\n\n### 1. 安装依赖\n\n```bash\n{{installCommand}}\n```\n\n### 2. 配置环境变量\n\n```bash\ncp .env.example .env\n# 编辑 .env 文件，填入数据库连接等配置\n```\n\n### 3. 启动开发服务器\n\n```bash\n{{startCommand}}\n```\n\n### 4. 访问应用\n\n打开浏览器访问：http://localhost:3000\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 运行测试\n\n```bash\nnpm test\n```\n\n---\n\n## ❓ 常见问题\n\n### Q: 数据库连接失败？\nA: 检查 .env 中的 DATABASE_URL 配置\n\n### Q: 端口被占用？\nA: 修改 .env 中的 PORT 环境变量\n\n---\n\n_由 Project X-Ray 生成 🦴_\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 测试策略\n\n### 单元测试示例\n\n```javascript\n// test/tech-stack-detector.test.js\nconst TechStackDetector = require('../lib/tech-stack-detector');\n\ndescribe('TechStackDetector', () => {\n  it('should detect Node.js project', async () => {\n    const detector = new TechStackDetector('./test/fixtures/node-project');\n    const result = await detector.detect();\n    expect(result.language).toBe('TypeScript/JavaScript');\n    expect(result.framework).toBe('NestJS');\n  });\n\n  it('should detect Java project', async () => {\n    const detector = new TechStackDetector('./test/fixtures/java-project');\n    const result = await detector.detect();\n    expect(result.language).toBe('Java');\n    expect(result.configFiles).toContain('pom.xml');\n  });\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 性能优化建议\n\n1. **文件扫描优化** - 使用流式读取，避免一次性加载大文件\n2. **依赖分析优化** - 缓存解析结果，避免重复解析\n3. **并行处理** - 文件扫描和代码行数统计并行执行\n4. **增量分析** - 支持只分析变更的文件\n\n---\n\n## 🔐 安全注意事项\n\n- 不执行项目中的任何代码\n- 不读取 .env 文件的实际内容（只提示存在）\n- 不上传项目内容到外部\n- 忽略敏感文件（*.key, *.pem, .git/config 等）\n\n---\n\n_小虾 🦐 - Project X-Ray 实现指南_\n","path":"F:\\2025ideazdjx\\openClaw-project\\xiaoxia\\project-xray\\implementation-guide.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":52787,"output":4716,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57503,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772501348001}}
