{"type":"message","id":"1e8e1575","parentId":"3bdabcca","timestamp":"2026-03-03T03:09:13.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要添加 renderCodeNavigationWithAnalysis 方法，使用代码分析器生成实际的功能映射表来替换模板中的占位符。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_026eeff855f641db96ce344b","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\project-xray\\lib\\docgen.js","oldText":"  renderCodeNavigation(analysis) {\n    return `# ${analysis.projectName} - 代码导航地图\n\n---\n\n## 🗺️ 功能 - 文件映射表\n\n| 功能 | 文件路径 |\n|------|---------|\n{{#each modules}}\n| {{name}} 模块 | `{{path}}/` | {{files}} 个文件 |\n{{/each}}\n\n---\n\n## 📍 关键文件位置\n\n### 配置文件\n\n- `package.json` - 项目配置\n- `.env.example` - 环境变量示例\n{{#if hasTsConfig}}\n- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript 配置\n{{/if}}\n\n### 入口文件\n\n{{#each entryPoints}}\n- `{{file}}` - {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### 测试文件\n\n- `test/` 或 `tests/` - 测试目录\n- `*.test.ts` 或 `*.spec.ts` - 测试文件\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 如何查找\n\n### 想找 X 功能？\n\n1. 先看 `03-core-modules.md` 了解模块职责\n2. 根据职责定位到对应模块目录\n3. 在模块目录中查找具体实现\n\n### 想找 X 接口？\n\n1. 查找 `*.controller.ts` 文件\n2. 搜索路由定义（如 `@Get()`, `@Post()`）\n3. 追踪到对应的 service\n\n---\n\n_由 Project X-Ray 生成 🦴_\n`;\n  }","newText":"  /**\n   * 生成代码导航地图（带代码分析）\n   */\n  async renderCodeNavigationWithAnalysis(analysis) {\n    let content = `# ${analysis.projectName} - 代码导航地图\\n\\n---\\n\\n`;\n    content += `## 🗺️ 功能 - 文件映射表\\n\\n`;\n    content += `| 功能 | 文件路径 | 说明 |\\n`;\n    content += `|------|---------|------|\\n`;\n    \n    // 分析每个模块的功能\n    for (const module of analysis.modules || []) {\n      const features = await this.codeAnalyzer.generateFeatureMapping([module]);\n      for (const feature of features) {\n        content += `| ${feature.feature} | \\`${feature.file}\\` | ${feature.functions} 函数，${feature.apis} API |\\n`;\n      }\n    }\n    \n    content += `\\n---\\n\\n`;\n    content += `## 📍 关键文件位置\\n\\n`;\n    content += `### 配置文件\\n\\n`;\n    content += `- \\`package.json\\` - 项目配置\\n`;\n    content += `- \\`.env.example\\` - 环境变量示例\\n\\n`;\n    content += `### 入口文件\\n\\n`;\n    for (const ep of analysis.entryPoints || []) {\n      content += `- \\`${ep.file}\\` - ${ep.description}\\n`;\n    }\n    \n    return content;\n  }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":185252,"output":779,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":186031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772507345886}}
